  "content": "Heartburn Organic Tea Price Rs. 964.57 Soothe Your Digestive Calmly Experience natural digestive relief with Heartburn Organic Tea, a soothing herbal blend crafted to calm discomfort and support gut balance. This caffeine-free tea is made with 100% organic, ethically sourced ingredients, delivering a smooth, comforting flavor with every cup. Designed for those seeki What's Inside Organic Herbal Blend: Supports digestion by combining nutrient-rich botanicals that work together to reduce occasional heartburn, promoting overall gut comfort Calming Digestive Support: Helps soothe the stomach and ease discomfort after meals, making it ideal for daily wellness routines Spearmint leaf Infusion: Naturally helps relax the digestive tract and reduce bloating, promoting a more comfortable stomach after meals Lemon Balm Leaf Blend: Supports digestive calm and helps ease tension in the gut, contributing to improved overall digestion Chamomile Flowers: Known for soothing properties that help reduce irritation and promote a calm, settled stomach Marshmallow Root Extract: Forms a gentle coating in the digestive system to help protect and soothe irritation for lasting comfort Raspberry Leaf: Supports digestive balance while adding subtle flavor, enhancing both effectiveness and taste Naturally Flavorful Taste: Delivers a pleasant flavor profile, making it easy to enjoy regularly without bitterness Versatile Brew: Perfect for post-meal relaxation or daily digestive support, fitting seamlessly into your lifestyle Why You'll Love It 17 cups (35g) per bag Premium loose-leaf blend Small-batch herbal formulation Caffeine-free Ethically sourced ingredients How to Use Add 2g of loose leaf tea to 8oz hot water Add 2g of loose leaf tea to 8oz hot water Steep for 5–7 minutes Steep for 5–7 minutes ",
